1	/// Admin scope isolation test suite.
2	///
3	/// Covers: scope resolution logic, 403 for out-of-scope users/orders,
4	/// super-admin unrestricted access, and district-to-campus expansion.
5	///
6	/// Run all (no DB needed):
7	///   cd backend && cargo test --test admin_scope_tests
8	///
9	/// Run DB-required integration tests (set TEST_DATABASE_URL first):
10	///   cd backend && cargo test --test admin_scope_tests -- --include-ignored
